    {% call components.columnTwoThirds() %}

        <p>The Fire Safety Order requires that fire safety training is provided to staff when they commence employment and that refresher training is provided on a regular basis.</p>

        <p>Fire is often the biggest safety risk any businesses ever has. Without fire safety training your insurances may not be valid and your staff are left vulnerable.</p>

        <p>Don't think a fire won't happen to you, last year there were over 33,000 recorded fires in UK businesses and community buildings. Protect your staff now and give them the best chance of escape if a fire does happen.</p>

        {{ components.heading(text='Learning outcomes', size='medium') }}

        <p>On completing this learning, you'll have knowledge of:</p>

        <ul class="list-bullet u-space-b30">
            <li>The common causes of fire</li>
